nodes.text: Backstab 33 was a French roleplaying magazine from September of 2001. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure which worked for both the West End Games D6 and Wizards of the Coast d20 roleplaying systems. The article was called "Étoiles, gardez-vous!... ...des jeunes gens idéalistes qui aiment trop le sport" and was written by Cyril Pasteu.
